title: Nois Cafe and Deli
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers authentic Vietnamese food, mostly organic and with a sustainability focus. There are four main dishes to select: baguette, soup (pho), rice rolls and salad; each one is available with quorn (vegetarian) or tofu (vegan). Also offers some vegan baked goods such as the traditional Swedish chocolate ball. Chef is aware of veganism and is accommodating to vegans.
